<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Order Confirmation - Psalms for kid</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        padding: 20px;
        width: 60%;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      h2 {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: greenyellow;
      }
      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
      }
      th,
      td {
        padding: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      p {
        margin-top: 10px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
          width: 100%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Thank you for your order!</h2>
      <p>Hi <%= order.user_name %>,</p>
      <p>This email confirms your recent order on Psalms for kid.</p>
      <p>Here are the details of your order:</p>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Order ID</th>
            <th>Course Name</th>
            <th>Qty</th>
            <th>Price</th>
            <th>Order Date</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>#<%= order._id %></td>
            <td><%= order.name %></td>
            <td>1</td>
            <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
            <td><%= order.date %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td></td>
            <td></td>
            <td>Subtotal =</td>
            <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <p>
        We hope you enjoy your new course! If you have any questions, please
        don't hesitate to contact us.
      </p>
      <p>Sincerely,</p>
      <p>Psalms for kid</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
